# ─── NOTE: styles/glass-theme.css is intentionally committed ──────────────────
# OJS production servers do not run Node build steps.
# The compiled CSS must be present in the repo for deployment.
# styles/glass-theme.css  ← do NOT add this

# ─── Tailwind source partials (not needed at runtime) ─────────────────────────
# tailwind.css is source only; the compiled output is styles/glass-theme.css
# If you want to exclude the source from the deployed plugin:
